_sText: Be sure to tell me what you think!  This is my first map that I'm releasing so I really value your opinion.  This map was made for the Gun Game mod so it has no buy zones.  In Gun Game, the player starts out with nothing but a glock.  When they get a kill with that gun, they level up to the usp.  Players continue to level up until level 24 when the player must get a kill with a knife.
